I ſhall cloſe all with the words of the Apoſtle;
Heb. 13.7. 
               Remember him that had the Rule over you, that ſo often ſpake to you the word of God; whoſe Faith follow, conſidering the end of his Converſation. And conſider his End aright, ſo that you may all fall in with ſhe Exhortation of our Saviour in my Text, To be always ready; For the Son of man may come upon you, as he did upon him, in an hour when you think not.
